official_title: To provide for the temporary use of certain lands in the city of South Gate, California, for elementary school purposes.

summary.text: Authorizes the city of South Gate, California, to extend for up to eight years from the date of enactment of this Act the existing lease between it and the Los Angeles Unified School District for use as an elementary school until the permanent relocation of Tweedy Elementary School.
